    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka: Student Activist Wasantha Mudalige held under Detention Orders",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Sri Lanka Police said that the Convener of the Inter-University Student's Federation and two others will be held for questioning under detention orders.",
        "The Office of the Police Media Division said that Venerable Galwewa Siridhamma Thero, and Bhashantha Jeewantha Gunathilake will be held under detention orders, in addition to Wasantha Mudalige, the Inter-University Student's Federation.",
        "They are being held for the investigations taking place on the events that transpired at the Aragalaya since the 9th of April 2022.",
        "The trio was among the 19 people who were arrested by Sri Lanka Police on Thursday (18) evening following a protest in Colombo.",
        "All of them were arrested for being party to unlawful assembly.",
        "Sri Lanka Police said that the suspects were arrested by the Cinnamon Gardens, Slave Island, and Borella Police Stations, and the Kelaniya Crimes Division.",
        "16 of the suspects were releaed on bail by the Colombo Additional Magistrate's Court.",
        "Sri Lanka: Student Activist Wasantha Mudalige held under Detention Orders",
        "Photographed Horton Plains leopards not a threat, Visitor not allowed to enter said area"
